  "StockRole": "Security Mech",
  "YangsThoughts": "Nimakachi built this one specifically for the Draconis Combine as a security mech. Saw a lot of use keeping Rasalhague worlds in line before they got their independence. Has a real ugly reputation honestly. The Fluid Gun was supposed to be non-lethal but that's not really how it played out in practice. Fell out of favor after the Clan Invasion when actual BattleMechs started costing the same. Production came back during the Jihad when parts got scarce.",
